snippet.title: Lies of P - 12 Minutes of Gameplay | gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Check out 12 minutes of Lies of P gameplay, taken straight from the floor of Gamescom 2022. Lies of P is an upcoming dark take on the story of Pinocchio in the form of a Bloodborne inspired soulslike.

#IGN #Gaming #LiesOfP
